when I've said to you

20:02.763 --> 20:05.032
"Slow down! Don't rush
into things with this girl."

20:05.152 --> 20:07.746
you haven't listened to me
a single damn time.

20:09.744 --> 20:12.215
Your heart is both
drunk and a kid.

20:17.567 --> 20:20.304
- Thanks for sticking up for me, man.
- That's what I do.

20:23.827 --> 20:26.480
Can I... Can I tell you some
of the ideas I have?

20:26.929 --> 20:27.970
Yeah.

20:29.026 --> 20:30.982
And, kids, Marshall was right.

20:31.102 --> 20:32.917
I didn't give up
on my dream house

20:33.037 --> 20:35.175
because that's the thing
about stupid decisions:

20:35.384 --> 20:36.716
